so%20investors%20won't%20care%20about%20the%20disintegrating%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarner-bros-discovery-9-billion-tv-networks-breakup-merger-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20told%20investors%20its%20TV%20business%20was%20in%20free-fall%2C%20and%20that%20it%20would%20take%20a%20%249%20billion%20writedown%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20those%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20it%20was%20Paramount's%20turn%3A%20The%20entertainment%20conglomerate%2C%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-ellison-paramount-ceo-skydance-larry-ellison-son-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20to%20be%20acquired%20by%20David%20Ellison%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20consortium%20of%20investors%2C%20just%20took%20a%20%246%20billion%20charge%20on%20its%20TV%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20context%3A%20Public%20investors%20value%20all%20of%20Paramount's%20equity%20at%20%247%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount's%20press%20release%20barely%20acknowledges%20the%20writedown%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.paramount.com%2Fstatic-files%2Fe1d635aa-b744-4965-96d0-1b7fbc0faf1f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit's%20first%20referenced%20in%20a%20tiny%20print%20footnote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20company's%20earnings%20call%2C%20Paramount%20management%20said%20part%20of%20the%20writedown%20is%20a%20bookkeeping%20necessity%20to%20even%20out%20what%20the%20company%20had%20previously%20thought%20its%20TV%20business%20was%20worth%2C%20and%20the%20value%20implied%20by%20Ellison's%20pending%20acquisition.%20But%20the%20broad%20strokes%20echo%20what%20WBD%20was%20suggesting%20earlier%3A%20The%20cable%20TV%20networks%20that%20once%20powered%20Paramount%20%E2%80%94%20MTV%2C%20Comedy%20Central%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%94%20are%20in%20permanent%20decline%2C%20even%20as%20they%20continue%20to%20throw%20off%20lots%20of%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount's%20TV%20networks%20(including%20CBS%2C%20which%20wasn't%20part%20of%20the%20markdown)%20saw%20their%20overall%20revenue%20decline%2017%25%20in%20the%20last%20quarter.%20Ads%20were%20down%2011%25%2C%20affiliate%20and%20subscriber%20fees%20were%20down%205%25%2C%20and%20licensing%20fees%20fell%20by%20half.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20that%20business%20still%20generated%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20in%20operating%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Paramount%20says%2C%20just%20like%20WBD%2C%20that%20it's%20making%20progress%20on%20its%20digital%20business%2C%20which%20is%20up%20and%20to%20the%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20difference%20between%20WBD%20and%20Paramount%20is%20that%20Paramount%20has%20already%20agreed%20to%20be%20sold%20%E2%80%94%20most%20likely%20to%20Ellison%2C%20unless%20a%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fdeals%2Fmystery-bidder-paramount-global-raises-questions-2024-08-01%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DApex%2520issued%2520a%2520press%2520release%2Cwith%2520David%2520Ellison%2527s%2520Skydance%2520Media.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%3C%2Fa%3E)%20bidder%20emerges%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%20So%20people%20who%20own%20Paramount%20shares%20won't%20care%20about%20these%20results%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20Ellison's%20problem%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-6-billion-loss-tv-networks-david-ellison-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723151175000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b52cbc5da406397bf45787%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-6-billion-loss-tv-networks-david-ellison-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Like%20WBD%2C%20but%20a%20little%20smaller.%20Unlike%20WBD%2C%20investors%20aren't%20going%20to