%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20video%2C%20Ghost%20Robotics'%20Vision%2060%20Q-UGV%20features%20a%20small%20turret%2C%20which%20holds%20the%20rifle%2C%20a%20targeting%20system%2C%20and%20a%20GoPro-like%20camera%20mounted%20on%20the%20front%20of%20its%20body.%20According%20to%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20rifle%20was%20AI-enabled%2C%20potentially%20for%20automated%20targeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20to%20look%20similar%20to%20other%20robotic%20dogs%20developed%20by%20the%20Army%20and%20other%20branches%20of%20the%20US%20military.%20Previous%20testing%20of%20such%20systems%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.army.mil%2Farticle%2F274841%2Fpromising_experiment_signals_future_integration_of_advanced_tech_into_army_units%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20activity%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20which%20an%20Army%20light%20infantry%20company%2C%20accompanied%20by%20robotic%20dogs%20and%20UAVs%20to%20scout%20and%20sense%20surroundings%2C%20explored%20a%20simulated%20urban%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20goals%20of%20Operation%20Hard%20Kill%2C%20the%20robotic%20dog%20was%20tested%20in%20a%20counter-drone%20role%2C%20mainly%20meant%20to%20identify%20and%20destroy%20unmanned%20aerial%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20further%20details%20aren't%20clear%2C%20Operation%20Hard%20Kill's%20exercises%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20focused%20on%20two%20core%20issues%20facing%20the%20Pentagon%3A%20the%20need%2C%20they%20say%2C%20to%20rapidly%20develop%20drone%20technologies%20at%20great%20scale%20and%20the%20capability%20to%20effectively%20defeat%20drones%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Defense%20Department's%20major%20Replicator%20Initiative%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FNews-Stories%2FArticle%2FArticle%2F3657609%2Fdefense-innovation-official-says-replicator-initiative-remains-on-track%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevealed%20last%20fall%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20focus