0we%20booked%20a%20cab%20for%20them.%20My%20coaches%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20cash%20and%20due%20to%20the%20language%20issues%2C%20led%20to%20an%20argument%20with%20the%20taxi%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20they%20came%20to%20collect%20some%20Euros%20from%20the%20hotel%20room%2C%20it%20took%20some%20time%20and%20led%20to%20the%20situation.%20I%20already%20have%20had%20a%20bad%20time%2C%20please%20don't%20spread%20rumours.%20Please%20support%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723140420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F1ief7gco_antim_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fdari-hui-hai-distressed-antim-panghal-leaves-paris-amid-olympic-games-village-entry-controversy-6295460%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sporting%20her%20Team%20India%20jersey%2C%20Antim%20Panghal%20along%20with%20four%20members%20of%20her%20team%20quietly%20did%20the%20check%20in%20at%20the%20Terminal%202C%20of%20the%20Charles%20de%20Gaulle%20Airport%20before%20boarding%20the%20Air%20India%20142%20flight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deepika%20flaunts%20her%20baby%20bump%20as%20she%20steps%20out%20with%20mom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723140230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112384070%2Cimgsize-86406.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmommy-to-be-deepika-padukone-flaunts-her-baby-bump-in-a-multi-coloured-floral-outfit-as-she-steps-out-with-her-mother-ujjala-padukone-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F112384070.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112384070.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDeepik