Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fryuichi-sakamoto-opus-album-last-emperor-1236097916%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fryuichi-sakamoto-opus-album-last-emperor-1236097916%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak's%20ISI%20Fuelling%20Unrest%20In%20Bangladesh%2C%20Claims%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20Son%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%2C%20who%20quit%20as%20prime%20minister%20and%20fled%20Bangladesh%2C%20will%20be%20back%20in%20the%20country%20as%20soon%20as%20democracy%20is%20restored%2C%20his%20son%20Sajeeb%20Wazed%20Joy%20said%20on%20Thursday%20and%20blamed%20Pakistan's%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20ISI%2C%20for%20fuelling%20the%20ongoing%20unrest%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20PTI%2C%20Mr%20Joy%20said%20that%20although%2076-year-old%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20would%20return%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%20it%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20decided%20whether%20she%20will%20be%20back%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bretired%20or%20active%26quot%3B%20politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asserted%20that%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Sheikh%20Mujib%20(Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman)%20family%20will%20neither%20abandon%20its%20people%20nor%20leave%20the%20beleaguered%20Awami%20League%20in%20the%20lurch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20for%20protecting%20his%20mother%20and%20appealed%20to%20India%20to%20help%20build%20international%20opinion%20and%20exert%20pressure%20to%20restore%20democracy%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20I%20had%20said%20she%20wouldn't%20return%20to%20Bangladesh.%20But%20a%20lot%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20last%20two%20days%20following%20continuous%20attacks%20on%20our%20leaders%20and%20party%20workers%20across%20the%20country.%20Now%20we%20are%20going%20to%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20keep%20our%20people%20safe%3B%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20leave%20them%20alone.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAwami%20League%20is%20the%20largest%20and%20oldest%20political%20party%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20so%20we%20cannot%20just%20walk%20away%20from%20our%20people.%20She%20will%20definitely%20return%20to%20Bangladesh%20once%20democracy%20is%20restored%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI%20over%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20Awami%20League%20an%20%26quot%3Ball-weather%20ally%20of%20India%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20India%20must%20ensure%20the%20security%20of%20Awami%20League%20leaders%20in%20Bangladesh%20by%20building%20international%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Joy%20also%20urged%20the%20interim%20government%2C%20headed%20by%20Nobel%20laureate%20Mohammad%20Yunus%2C%20to%20restore%20law%20and%20order%2C%20noting%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20country%20is%20turning%20into%20a%20state%20of%20anarchy%20and%20becoming%20a%20second%20Afghanistan%20in%20the%20region.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20he%20also%20expects%20the%20interim%20government%20to%20create%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20whenever%20democracy%20is%20restored%20and%20fresh%20elections%20are%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20exclude%20the%20Awami%20League%20and%20have%20a%20representative%20democracy%20in%20Bangladesh%20ever.%20Whatever%20his%20(Mohammed%20Yunus)%20personal%20views%20are%2C%20he%20has%20said%20that%20he%20wants%20a%20government%20of%20unity%20and%20wants%20to%20move%20forward%20and%20not%20let%20the%20mistakes%20of%20the%20past%20cloud%20over%20the%20future.%20I%20hope%20he%20stays%20true%20to%20his%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf%20Yunus%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20head%20of%20Bangladesh's%20interim%20government%20on%20Thursday%20and%20was%20administered%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20by%20President%20Mohammed%20Shahabuddin%20at%20a%20ceremony%20in%20Dhaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20resigned%20and%20fled%20the%20country%20following%20violent%20protests%20against%20her%20government%20over%20a%20controversial%20quota%20system%20in%20jobs.%20She%20flew%20to%20the%20Hindon%20air%20base%2C%20near%20Delhi%2C%20in%20a%20Bangladesh%20military%20aircraft%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Joy%20mentioned%20that%20once%20democracy%20is%20restored%2C%20either%20the%20Awami%20League%20or%20BNP%20will%20come%20to%20power%2C%20and%20the%20%26quot%3BMujib%20family%20and%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20will%20be%20around.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20all%20our%20party%20leaders%20for%20the%20last%20two%20days.%20My%20mother%20was%20going%20to%20retire%20anytime%20soon%2C%20so%20we%20thought%20now%20that%20she%20is%20gone%2C%20they%20(rioters)%20would%20leave%20our%20party%20people%20alone%2C%20but%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20Instead%2C%20they%20started%20attacking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeclining%20to%20comment%20directly%20on%20whether%20he%20and%20his%20sister%20Saima%20Wazed%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20the%20South%20East%20Asian%20regional%20director%20for%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%2C%20would%20enter%20politics%2C%20Joy%20said%20he%20would%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20protect%20Bangladesh%20from%20total%20anarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20give%20a%20definite%20reply%20to%20this%20question.%20But%20I%20will%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20save%20Bangladesh%20and%20protect%20the%20Awami%20League.%20The%20Mujib%20family%20would%20not%20leave%20them%20in%20a%20lurch%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joy%2C%20the%20former%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20Advisor%20to%20Hasina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlaming%20Pakistan%20for%20fueling%20the%20unrest%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20Joy%20said%20there%20is%20circumstantial%20evidence%20suggesting%20foreign%20interference%20and%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Pakistan's%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20quite%20certain%20given%20the%20circumstantial%20evidence%3B%20I%20suspect%20Pakistan%20ISI's%20involvement.%20The%20attacks%20and%20protests%20were%20very%20coordinated%2C%20meticulously%20planned%2C%20and%20intentional%20efforts%20to%20keep%20inflaming%20the%20situation%20through%20social%20media.%20No%20matter%20what%20the%20government%20did%20to%20control%20the%20situation%2C%20they%20kept%20trying%20to%20worsen%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20rioters%20attacked%20police%20with%20guns%20which%20could%20only%20be%20provided%20by%20terror%20outfits%20and%20foreign%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20reports%20of%20involvement%20of%20a%20US%20intelligence%20agency%20like%20the%20CIA%2C%20Joy%20said%20he%20had%20no%20evidence%20but%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bmaybe%2C%20they%20are%26quot%3B.%20He%20dismissed%20any%20Chinese%20involvement%20when%20asked%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20reports%20of%20Hasina%20seeking%20asylum%20in%20the%20UK%20or%20any%20other%20country%20as%20%26quot%3Brumours%26quot%3B%2C%20Joy%20said%20the%20reports%20of%20her%20US%20Visa%20being%20revoked%20are%20also%20untrue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20of%20this%20sort%20has%20been%20planned%20(seeking%20asylum).%20Sooner%20or%20later%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20restoration%20of%20democracy%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20hopefully%2C%20that%20will%20be%20between%20the%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20(BNP)%20and%20Awami%20League.%20Then%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20will%20be%20back.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20she%20wants%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Bangladesh.%20It's%20a%20question%20of%20when%20rather%20than%20if%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20hinting%20that%20the%20ousted%20Bangladesh%20PM%20will%20be%20staying%20at%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20India%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoy%2C%20who%20spent%20much%20of%20his%20childhood%20studying%20in%20India%2C%20appealed%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20ensure%20the%20quick%20restoration%20of%20democracy%20for%20stability%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20protecting%20my%20mother.%20I%20owe%20my%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20If%20India%20wants%20stability%20in%20its%20eastern%20backyard%2C%20then%20they%20have%20to%20pressure%20the%20international%20community%20and%20take%20the%20lead%20to%20ensure%20the%20quick%20restoration%20of%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20'INDIA-out'%20campaign%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20anti-India%20forces%20are%20already%20very%20active%2C%20and%20with%20Awami%20League%20out%20of%20power%2C%20the%20ISI%20is%20now%20free%20to%20supply%20as%20many%20weapons%20as%20it%20wants%20to%20the%20anti-India%20forces.%26quot%3B%20Joy%20said%20India%20must%20act%20fast%20before%20anti-India%20forces%20gain%20more%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERefuting%20claims%20that%20Ms%20Hasina%20ran%20away%20to%20save%20her%20own%20life%2C%20he%20said%20the%20family%20insisted%20on%20stopping%20the%20bloodshed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20not%20willing%20to%20leave%20the%20country.%20The%20Prime%20Minister's%20security%20was%20ready%20to%20protect%20her%20till%20the%20end.%20But%20that%20would%20have%20led%20to%20hundreds%20of%20deaths%20of%20protestors%20who%20were%20marching%20towards%20the%20PM's%20residence.%20We%20convinced%20her%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20we%20cannot%20let%20her%20get%20killed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20was%20not%20weak%2C%20but%20my%20mother%20did%20not%20want%20to%20harm%20the%20students.%20Even%20after%20her%20leaving%20the%20country%2C%20the%20bloodshed%20has%20not%20stopped.%20The%20people%20will%20now%20understand%20the%20difference%20with%20and%20without%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dea