0and%20led%20to%20him%20being%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bbanker%20to%20the%20poor%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoverty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus'%20belief%20that%20poverty%20-%20which%20plagued%20more%20than%2018%25%20of%20Bangladesh's%20population%20in%202022%20-%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%26quot%3B%20and%20causes%20problems%20ranging%20from%20terrorism%20to%20trafficking%2C%20informs%20most%20of%20his%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20leave%20people%20poor%20and%20live%20happily...they%20are%20in%20a%20desperate%20situation.%20When%20you%20are%20desperate%2C%20you%20disturb%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yunus%20told%20Nobelprize.org%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%20that%20he%20sought%20to%20inculcate%20%26quot%3Bsound%20financial%20principles%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20poor%20through%20his%20microcredit%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobalisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus%20has%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Bmulti-national%20social%20businesses%26quot%3B%20that%20either%20give%20the%20poor%20ownership%20or%20keep%20profits%20within%20poor%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20dabbled%20in%20politics%20in%202007%2C%20he%20suggested%20upgrading%20the%20Chittagong%20port%20to%20a%20continental%20seaport%20-%20a%20plan%20critics%20said%20could%20endanger%20national%20security%2C%20jobs%20and%20the%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus%20also%20spoke%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20civilisation%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20The%20Indian%20Express%20newspaper%20last%20week%2C%20in%20which%20he%20criticised%20India%20for%20saying%20the%20upheaval%20in%20Bangladesh%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Binternal%20matter%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20the%20chaos%20could%20spill%20over%20to%20its%20neighbours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiplomacy%20has%20a%20much%20richer%20vocabulary%20than%20saying%20it%20is%20their%20internal%20affair%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus%20emphasises%20the%20role%20of%20women%20in%20building%20the%20future%20and%20has%20been%20part%20of%20multiple%20international%20commissions%20catering%20to%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20currently%20outnumber%20men%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20constitute%2097%25%20of%20Grameen%20Bank's%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20want%20to%20build%20up%20something%20for%20the%20future%20with%20their%20money.%20Men%20want%20to%20spend%20it%20enjoying%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Harvard%20Business%20Review%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723135380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F56nalei8_muhammad-yunus_625x300_08_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-is-bangladeshs-caretaker-leader-muhammad-yunus-economic-thinking-6294710%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nobel%20Peace%20Prize-winning%20economist%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20takes%20over%20as%20the%20head%20of%20Bangladesh's%20caretaker%20government%20on%20Thursday%20when%20the%20country%20is%20facing%20tough%20economic%20challenges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-is-bangladeshs-caretaker-leader-muhammad-yunus-economic-thinking-6294710%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20we%20know%20about%20military%20records%20of%20Walz%20and%20Vance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723134857000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F5c06%2Flive%2F2e6d8e60-5593-11ef-b2d2-cdb23d5d7c5b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%