itted%20by%20its%20operator.Stealthy%20and%20agile%2C%20they%20could%20soon%20become%20an%20invaluable%20ally%20on%20the%20front%20line%20for%20an%20Ukrainian%20army%20that%20is%20short%20on%20manpower%20to%20repel%20the%20Russian%20invasion%2C%20its%20makers%20said.Low%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20therefore%20difficult%20to%20detect%2C%20the%20robot%20dogs%20can%20use%20thermal%20imaging%20to%20inspect%20enemy%20trenches%20or%20the%20inside%20of%20buildings%20in%20combat%20zones.%26quot%3BWe%20have%20surveillance%20soldiers%20who%20get%20sent%20on%20reconnaissance%20missions%20(who)%20are%20most%20of%20the%20time%20very%20highly%20trained%20people%2C%20very%20experienced%20people%20(and)%20always%20exposed%20to%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20operator%20who%20called%20himself%20%26quot%3BYuri%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20he%20showed%20it%20off%20to%20AFP%20journalists.%26quot%3BThis%20dog%20limits%20the%20risk%20for%20soldiers%20and%20increases%20operational%20capabilities.%20This%20is%20the%20core%20function%20of%20the%20dog%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20operator%2C%20who%20works%20for%20a%20British%20company%20providing%20military%20equipment.A%20more%20advanced%20model%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BBAD%20Two%26quot%3B%20could%20not%20be%20shown%20for%20security%20reasons.The%20device%20used%20in%20the%20demonstration%20has%20a%20battery%20that%20powers%20it%20for%20around%20two%20hours.Useful%20for%20detecting%20mines%20or%20improvised%20explosive%20devices%2C%20the%20robot%20dog%20can%20also%20be%20used%20to%20carry%20up%20to%20seven%20kilos%20(15%20pounds)%20of%20ammunition%20or%20medicines%20to%20hot%20spots%20on%20the%20battlefield.%26quot%3BI%20can't%20say%20how%20many%20we%20deployed%26quot%3B%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Yuri%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20will%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20operations%20and%20increase%20the%20safety%20of%20soldiers.%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20the%20robot%20dogs%20were%20ever%20to%20fall%20into%20Russian%20hands%2C%20he%20said%2C%20an%20emergency%20switch%20allows%20the%20operator%20to%20erase%20all%20its%20data.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fnext-gen-war-robots-ukraine-set-to-deploy-bad-one-dogs-for-recon-missions-and-mine-detection%2Fphotostory%2F112382442.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fnext-gen-war-robots-ukraine-set-to-deploy-bad-one-dogs-for-recon-missions-and-mine-detection%2Famp_etphotostory%2F112382442.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fnext-gen-war-robots-ukraine-set-to-deploy-bad-one-dogs-for-recon-missions-and-mine-detection%2Famp_etphotostory%2F112382442.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSarpanch%20Sahab%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Special%20Call%20To%20Hockey%20Captain%20Harmanpreet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20congratulated%20the%20Indian%20men's%20hockey%20team%20on%20its%20bronze%20medal%20success%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%20India%20captain%20Harmanpreet%20Singh%20scored%20twice%20as%20India%20beat%20Spain%202-1%20in%20the%20bronze%20medal%20match%20at%20Stade%20Yves-du-Manoir%20on%20Thursday.%20Marc%20Miralles%20had%20pulled%20Spain%20in%20front%20after%20converting%20a%20penalty%20stroke%20in%20the%2018th%20minute.%20However%2C%20Harmanpreet%20equalised%20in%20the%20dying%20embers%20of%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20before%20grabbing%20his%20second%20three%20minutes%20into%20the%20third%20quarter.%20Despite%20Spain's%20all-out%20attack%20in%20last%20five%20minutes%20of%20the%20final%20quarter%2C%20India%20held%20on%20for%20a%20famous%20win%20and%20clinced%20the%20fourth%20medal%20for%20the%20country%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Olympics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20match%2C%20PM%20Modi%20called%20the%20Indian%20hockey%20team%20to%20congratulate%20the%20players%20for%20their%20success.%20During%20the%20phone%20call%2C%20PM%20Modi%20spoke%20with%20captain%20Harmanpreet%20and%20goalkeeper%20PR%20Sreejesh%2C%20who%20was%20played%20his%20final%20game%20for%20India%20in%20the%20bronze%20medal%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20phone%20call%2C%20Modi%20called%20Harmanpreet%20as%20%26quot%3BSarpanch%26quot%3B%20(leader).%20Harmanpreet%20has%20been%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BSarpanch%26quot%3B%20for%20leading%20the%20team%20from%20the%20front%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20ending%20the%20tournament%20with%2010%20goals%2C%20including%20two%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20asked%20the%20retiring%20Sreejesh%20to%20help%20groom%20a%20team%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20spoke%20to%20the%20Indian%20Hockey%20team%20and%20congratulated%20them%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBronze%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Bronze%3C%2Fa%3E%20medal%20victory.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FOlympicGames%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23OlympicGames%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FParis2024%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Paris2024%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOuuaEHVj0y%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOuuaEHVj0y%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1821567225670901771%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20this%20is%20India's%20fourth%20bronze%20medal%2C%20and%20second%20in%20succession%20following%20Tokyo%2C%20and%20adds%20to%20those%20eight%20golds%2C%20the%20last%20of%20which%20came%20in%201980%2C%20and%20three%20silvers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20won%20seven%20of%20their%20previous%2010%20encounters%20with%20three-time%20champions%20Spain%20but%20after%20a%20cagey%20first%20half%20they%20found%20themselves%20trailing%20when%20Miralles%20fired%20an%2018th%20minute%20penalty%20stroke%20past%20the%20'Wall%20of%20India'%20Sreejesh%20Raveendran%2C%20playing%20his%20336th%20and%20final%20international.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorja%20Lacalle%20almost%20made%20it%20two%2C%20beating%20Sreejesh%20only%20to%20see%20his%20shot%20rebound%20off%20the%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20began%20to%20press%20hard%20and%20with%20just%20a%20few%20seconds%20remaining%20of%20the%20first%20half%2C%20Harmanpreet%20buried%20a%20penalty%20corner%20to%20level%20the%20scores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20minutes%20after%20the%20break%2C%20Harmanpreet%20repeated%20the%20trick%2C%20sweeping%20another%20penalty%20corner%20just%20inside%20the%20Spanish%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorld%20champions%20Germany%20were%20scheduled%20to%20face%20Netherlands%20in%20the%20gold%20medal%20match%20later%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20ANI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723132920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fbbk608k8_harmanpreet-singh_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fsarpanch-sahab-pm-narendra-modis-special-call-to-india-hockey-captain-harmanpreet-singh-is-viral-6294591%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20congratulated%20the%20Indian%20men's%20hockey%20team%20on%20its%20bronze%20medal%20success%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fsarpanch-sahab-pm-narendra-modi