rfect%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20close%20to%20nature%20and%20enjoy%20mountain%20treks.%20The%20area%E2%80%99s%20quiet%20charm%20and%20its%20closeness%20to%20their%20old%20place%20in%20Devikhal%20were%20also%20big%20pluses.%20Besides%2C%20they%20were%20confident%20that%20their%20loyal%20customers%20would%20make%20the%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201156px)%20100vw%2C%201156px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22They%20knew%20that%20Lansdowne%E2%80%99s%20dense%20forests%20were%20perfect%20for%20them.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958.jpeg%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958-271x300.jpeg%20271w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958-500x554.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958-768x850.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958-150x166.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThey%20knew%20that%20Lansdowne%E2%80%99s%20dense%20forests%20were%20perfect%20for%20them.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20knew%20moving%20their%20caf%C3%A9%20to%20hill%20stations%20like%20Nainital%20or%20Mussoorie%20would%20be%20pricey.%20And%20having%20previously%20visited%20Lansdowne%2C%20they%20found%20that