fish%20and%20chips%2C%20complemented%20by%20a%20range%20of%20other%20offerings%20including%20falafel%2C%20salami%20and%20sausage%20sandwiches%2C%20wraps%2C%20and%20chicken%20momos.%20They%20also%20offer%20up%20to%20six%20different%20Maggi%20varieties%20and%20seven%20types%20of%20omelettes.%20The%20fresh%20Singhara%20fish%20is%20a%20favourite%20among%20visitors.%20While%20salami%2C%20bacon%2C%20and%20pepperoni%20are%20kept%20frozen%2C%20all%20other%20items%20are%20made%20fresh%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20did%20they%20prioritise%20continental%20dishes%20over%20local%20cuisine%3F%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20introduce%20locals%20to%20a%20different%20dining%20experience%2C%20something%20that%20deviates%20from%20their%20local%20dining%20options.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%20serves%20a%20mix%20of%20Indian%20and%20continental%20foods%2C%20with%20chefs%20ensuring%20everything%20is%20prepared%20fresh.%20They%20start%20their%20day%20by%20making%20fresh%20tomato%20puree%2C%20and%20patrons%20have%20grown%20fond%20of%20the%20variety%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBoosted%20revenue%20for%20nearby%20shops%20and%20offered%20opportunities%20to%20locals%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20couple%20first%20arrived%20in%20Lansdowne%2C%20they%20struggled%20to%20find%20ingredients%20like%20thyme%2C%20oregano%2C%20salami%2C%20and%20sausages.%20They%20had%20to%20import%20these%20items%20from%20Delhi%20in%20ice%20boxes.%20They%20now%20source%20most%20of%20their%20supplies%20from%20a%20small%20local%20shop%20called%20Dhobi%20Ghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20shop%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20deep%20freezer%2C%20Amit%20transports%20the%20ingredients%20to%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20arrive.%20The%20shop%2C%20noticing%20the%20success%20of%20these%20products%2C%20has%20started%20stocking%20cheese%2C%20mustard%20sauce%2C%20chocolate%20syrups%2C%20corn%20flour%2C%20and%20bread%20crumbs%E2