0Class%20X.%20He%20has%20also%20done%20a%20pipe%20fitter%20course%20from%20Mazagon%20Dock%20Limited.%20It%20was%20Gaurav's%20efforts%20due%20to%20which%20the%20police%20could%20understand%20the%20entire%20chain%20of%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20proud%20father%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723130340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F0htt5beg_india-police-generic_625x300_23_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbody-stuffed-in-bag-constables-speech-and-hearing-impaired-son-helps-with-murder-probe-6293442%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20speech%20and%20hearing%20impaired%20son%20of%20a%20constable%20used%20sign%20language%20to%20communicate%20with%20an%20accused%2C%20also%20suffering%20from%20the%20same%20disability%2C%20to%20help%20Mumbai%20police%20with%20their%20probe%20into%20a%20murder%20case%2C%20an%20official%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbody-stuffed-in-bag-constables-speech-and-hearing-impaired-son-helps-with-murder-probe-6293442%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20A%20Chinese%20Scholar%20Ran%20A%20Spy%20Ring%20In%20US%20For%20Decades%20Before%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Chinese-American%20scholar%2C%20who%20projected%20himself%20as%20a%20pro-democracy%20activist%2C%20has%20been%20convicted%20by%20a%20US%20court%20of%20using%20his%20reputation%20to%20gather%20information%20on%20dissidents%20and%20sharing%20it%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20jury%20in%20New%20York%20delivered%20the%20verdict%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20The%20Guardian%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2075-year-old%20lived%20a%20double%20life%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20China's%20main%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20State%20Security%2C%20the%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20opening%20statement%20last%20month%2C%20US%20attorney%20Ellen%20Sise%20said%20that%20Wang%20pretended%20to%20be%20opposed%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20close%20to%20people%20who%20were%20actually%20opposed%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20then%2C%20the%20defendant%20betrayed%20those%20people%2C%20people%20who%20trusted%20him%2C%20by%20reporting%20information%20on%20them%20to%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20Sise%20noted.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E'Plot%20of%20a%20spy%20novel'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWang%20was%20convicted%20of%20providing%20the%20contact%20information%20of%20prominent%20dissidents%20to%20the%20intelligence%20agency%20in%20his%20homeland.%20He%20further%20lied%20to%20federal%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20about%20the%20scheme.%20The%20jury%20found%20him%20guilty%20on%20four%20counts%20following%20the%20week-long%20trial%20in%20the%20Brooklyn%20federal%20court%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20indictment%20could%20have%20been%20the%20plot%20of%20a%20spy%20novel%2C%20but%20the%20evidence%20is%20shockingly%20real%2C%E2%80%9D%20Breon%20Peace%2C%20the%20US%20attorney%20for%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20New%20York%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWang%20was%20willing%20to%20betray%20those%20who%20respected%20and%20trusted%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Peace%20noted.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWang%20faces%20up%20to%2025%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20when%20he%20is%20to%20be%20sentenced%20on%20January%209%20next%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Shujun%20Wang%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWang%2C%20an%20American%20citizen%2C%20has%20been%20settled%20in%20New%20York%20since%20the%201990s%20after%20his%20stint%20as%20a%20visiting%20university%20scholar%20of%20East%20Asian%20studies%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20commemorate%20figures%20linked%20to%20the%201989%20Tiananmen%20Square%20uprising%2C%20he%20helped%20found%20a%20pro-democracy%20group%20in%202006%20in%20the%20Flushing%20neighbourhood%20of%20Queens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHu%20Yaobang%20and%20Zhao%20Ziyang%20Memorial%20Foundation%20is%20named%20for%20two%20leaders%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20in%20the%201980s.%20As%20per%20its%20official%20website%2C%20the%20group's%20mission%20is%20to%20promote%20China's%20%26quot%3Bconstitutional%20transformation.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20that%20Wang%20used%20his%20position%20and%20status%20among%20the%20Chinese%20community%20to%20act%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccovert%20intelligence%20asset%20in%20his%20own%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20since%20at%20least%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWang%2C%20according%20to%20the%20prosecutors%2C%20was%20ordered%20to%20collect%20information%20about%20topics%20and%20people%20the%20Chinese%20government%20deemed%20undesirable.%20Later%2C%20he%20passed%20on%20this%20information%20to%20his%20handlers%20via%20in-person%20meetings%20as%20well%20as%20written%20correspondence%2C%20including%20%E2%80%9Cdiaries%2C%E2%80%9D%20describing%20his%20interactions%20with%20prominent%20activists%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEllen%20Sise%2C%20in%20the%20opening%20statements%2C%20noted%20that%20Wang%20led%20a%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20life%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20portrayed%20himself%20as%20an%20academic%20and%20a%20pro-democratic%20activist...%20Appearances%20can%20be%20deceiving%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWang%20emigrated%20to%20the%20US%20in%201994.%20He%20was%20arrested%20by%20officials%20in%20March%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723129620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-0