hering%20complete%20information%20and%20preparing%20a%20report.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20the%20NDTV%20team%20for%20exposing%20this.%20NDTV%20has%20worked%20responsibly%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20wildlife%20and%20forest%20areas%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDTV%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20not%20only%20did%2034%20tigers%20die%20in%20the%20Bandhavgarh%20Tiger%20Reserve%20but%20there%20were%20also%20attempts%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20deaths%20by%20attributing%20them%20to%20fights%20among%20the%20big%20cats.%20In%20March%2C%20the%20Principal%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20formed%20a%20three-member%20committee%20to%20investigate%20these%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20NDTV%2C%20uncovered%20the%20following%20lapses%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVideography%20of%20postmortems%20was%20not%20conducted%20in%20all%20cases.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPreliminary%20Offence%20Report%20(POR)%20for%20tiger%20deaths%20was%20not%20recorded%20in%20most%20cases.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20was%20an%20absence%20of%20prescribed%20veterinarians%20for%20postmortems%2C%20and%20most%20parameters%20were%20not%20followed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEfforts%20to%20protect%20crime%20scenes%20were%20inadequate%2C%20and%20dog%20squads%20or%20metal%20detectors%20were%20not%20used.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESample%20collection%20and%20sealing%20were%20poorly%20handled%2C%20affecting%20the%20chain%20of%20custody%20during%20court%20cases.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECase%20diaries%20or%20documentation%20were%20often%20not%20prepared.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFinal%20NTCA%20reports%20were%20not%20submitted%20in%20several%20cases%20by%20officials%20from%20both%20the%20Bandhavgarh%20Tiger%20Reserve%20and%20Shahdol%20Forest%20Range.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMany%20cases%20of%20tiger%20deaths%20were%20superficially%20classified%20as%20infighting%20without%2