tory%2Famp%2Fmass-youtube-outage-in-russia-as-authorities-continue-crackdown-13193333%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Kerala%20Tragedy%20Is%20Why%20States%20Must%20Stop%20Opposing%20'ESA'%20Tags%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fujofpbng_wayanad-landslides_625x300_30_July_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20landslides%20in%20Wayanad%20have%20prompted%20the%20central%20government%20to%20act%20swiftly%20in%20designating%20Ecologically%20Sensitive%20Areas%20(ESA)%20in%20the%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20a%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20Site%20and%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20%26quot%3Bhottest%20hotspots%26quot%3B%20of%20biological%20diversity%20in%20the%20world.%20On%20July%2031%2C%20the%20central%20government%20issued%20the%20sixth%20iteration%20of%20the%20draft%20notification%2C%20proposing%20to%20declare%20over%2056%2C825.7%20square%20kilometres%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20across%20six%20states%20-%20Gujarat%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Goa%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Kerala%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20-%20as%20ESA.%20This%20includes%2013%20villages%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%2C%20which%20experienced%20a%20series%20of%20landslides%20on%20July%2030.%20Roughly%20400%20people%20died%20due%20to%20the%20landslides%2C%20while%20150%20still%20remain%20missing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government's%20decision%20reflects%20a%20realisation%20that%20designating%20the%20entire%20region%20as%20an%20ESA%20in%20one%20go%20might%20not%20be%20feasible.%20The%20new%20notification%20follows%20an%20older%20draft%20issued%20in%202022%2C%20which%20expired%20when%20the%20central%20government%20and%20the%20six%20states%20could%20not%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20ESA%20in%20their%20respective%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20draft%20proposes%20to%20designate%20449%20square%20kilometres%20in%20Gujarat%2C%2017%2C340%20square%20kilometres%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%201%2C461%20square%20kilometres%20in%20Goa%2C%2020%2C668%20square%20kilometres%20in%20Karnataka%2C%206%2C914%20square%20kilometres%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%209%2C993.7%20square%20kilometres%20in%20Kerala%20as%20ecologically%20sensitive.%20This%20step-by-step%20approach%20is%20largely%20due%20to%20a%20decade%20of%20failed%20attempts%20to%20achieve%20a%20consensus%20among%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20No%20Consensus%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Environment%20Ministry%20first%20issued%20a%20draft%20notification%20for%20the%20ESA%20in%20March%202014%2C%20based%20on%20recommendations%20from%20the%20High-Level%20Working%20Group%20(HLWG)%20established%20by%20the%20Central%20government%20in%202013.%20Headed%20by%20space%20scientist%20K.%20Kasturirangan%2C%20the%20HLWG%20reviewed%20the%20earlier%20recommendations%20of%202011%20made%20by%20the%20Madhav%20Gadgil-led%20expert%20committee%20on%20ESAs.%20While%20the%20Gadgil%20committee%20had%20recommended%20designating%2064%25%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20as%20ESA%2C%20the%20Kasturirangan%20panel%20proposed%20only%2037%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gadgil%20report%20included%20detailed%20landslide%20vulnerability%20mapping%20and%20identified%20villages%20prone%20to%20landslides.%20However%2C%20stakeholder%20states%20opposed%20these%20recommendations%2C%20arguing%20they%20were%20too%20restrictive%20and%20detrimental%20to%20development%20and%20livelihoods.%20Environmentalists%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20claim%20that%20state%20governments%20have%20faced%20pressure%20from%20vested%20interests%2C%20such%20as%20mining%20and%20tourism%20industries%2C%20to%20delay%20the%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMultiple%20stakeholders%20and%20propaganda%20by%20select%20players%20is%20hampering%20the%20consensus.%20A%20national%20policy%20may%20not%20translate%20to%20reality%20even%20though%20it%20has%20its%20scientific%20backing%20as%20local%20sentiments%20are%20often%20a%20sensitive%20subject%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20environmentalist%20Arun%20Krishnamurthy%2C%20founder%20of%20E.F.I%2C%20a%20Chennai-based%20NGO.%20%26quot%3BProlonged%20acceptance%20by%20state%20governments%20often%20correlates%20with%20grassroots%20acceptance%20of%20the%20proposed%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Karnataka%20objected%20to%20the%20proposed%20bans%20on%20mining%2C%20quarrying%2C%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%20new%20industries.%20Concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20in%20Kerala%2C%20where%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20population%20resides%20within%20or%20near%20the%20proposed%20buffer%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Thara%20KG%2C%20former%20head%20of%20the%20Disaster%20Management%20Centre%20in%20Kerala%2C%20highlights%20the%20state's%20challenges%3A%20high%20population%20density%2C%20livelihood%20concerns%2C%20and%20housing%20issues.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20resistance%20to%20the%20ESA%20from%20people%20who%20feel%20their%20immediate%20problems%20need%20addressing%20first.%20The%20entire%20state%20is%20vulnerable.%20%C2%A0When%20all%20districts%20in%20Kerala%20are%20multi-hazard-prone%20districts%2C%20where%20do%20you%20relocate%20people%3F%20The%20only%20remedy%20is%20to%20mitigate%20the%20vulnerability%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Thara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHastening%20The%20Process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202022%2C%20the%20Centre%20formed%20a%20new%20panel%20under%20former%20Director-General%20of%20Forests%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20states%20and%20resolve%20issues.%20This%20five-member%20expert%20panel%20is%20expected%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20by%20the%20end%20of%20next%20month%20and%20has%20been%20actively%20engaging%20with%20the%20six%20states%20to%20address%20inconsistencies%20and%20information%20gaps%20in%20the%20draft%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20draft%20includes%20proposals%20such%20as%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20mining%2C%20quarrying%2C%20and%20sand%20mining.%20Existing%20mines%20are%20to%20be%20phased%20out%20within%20five%20years%20from%20the%20final%20notification%20or%20the%20expiry%20of%20existing%20leases%2C%20whichever%20comes%20first.%20The%20draft%20also%20prohibits%20new%20thermal%20power%20projects%20while%20allowing%20existing%20projects%20to%20continue%20without%20expansion.%20It%20bans%20highly%20polluting%20industries%20(as%20specified%20by%20the%20State%20Pollution%20Control%20Board)%20and%20their%20expansion%2C%20and%20prohibits%20large-scale%20construction%20projects%20and%20townships%2C%20with%20exceptions%20for%20repairs%20and%20renovations%20of%20existing%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20suggest%20that%20many%20states%20have%20requested%20reductions%20in%20the%20ESA%20areas%20and%20adjustments%20to%20the%20inclusion%20or%20exclusion%20of%20certain%20villages.%20The%20draft%20specifies%20that%20agriculture%2C%20plantation%2C%20and%20less%20polluting%20activities%20will%20not%20be%20affected%20by%20ESA%20provisions%2C%20and%20the%20final%20area%20will%20be%20determined%20based%20on%20state%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landslides%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20as%20well%20as%20similar%20disasters%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20underscore%20the%20dangers%20posed%20by%20unscientific%20infrastructure%2C%20uncontrolled%20tourism%2C%20illegal%20mining%2C%20and%20habitation%20in%20eco-sensitive%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20repeated%20calamities%20are%20bringing%20us%20closer%20to%20reality.%20Building%20consensus%20requires%20cutting%20across%20political%20lines%20with%20science%20and%20logic%2C%20ensuring%20appropriate%20compensation%20for%20those%20affected%2C%20and%20avoiding%20compromises%20that%20favour%20powerful%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Krishnamurthy.%20He%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BDetailed%20community%20awareness%2C%20engagement%2C%20and%20a%20phased%2C%20results-oriented%20policy%20are%20crucial%20for%20conserving%20the%20Western%20Ghats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20debate%20between%20environmental%20conservation%20and%20development%20remains%20challenging%20as%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20find%20solutions%20that%20do%20not%20compromise%20either%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723121100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fujofpbng_wayanad-landslides_625x300_30_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkerala-landslide-tragedy-is-why-people-must-stop-opposing-esas-6293057%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20July%2031%2C%20the%20central%20government%20issued%20the%20sixth%20iteration%20of%20a%20draft%20notification%2C%20proposing%20to%20declare%20over%2056%2C825.7%20square%20kilometres%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20across%20six%20states%20as%20Ecologically%20Sensitive%20Areas%20(ESA).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkerala-landslide-tragedy-is-why-people-must-stop-opposing-esas-6293057%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unprecedented%20Ukrainian%20incursion%20into%20Russia%20signals%20new%20type%20of%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723120920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F08%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-ukraine-russia-kursk_6649709.jpg%3F20240807113017%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Funprecedented-ukrainian-incursion-into-russia-signals-new-type-of-attack-13193318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20momentary%