e%20from%20walks%20of%20life%20where%20sustainability%20is%20prided.%20And%20so%2C%20every%20nook%20of%20the%20resort%20is%20eco-conscious.%20Rainwater%20is%20harvested%20through%20aquifers%20%E2%80%94%20a%20body%20of%20rock%20and%20sediment%20that%20holds%20groundwater.%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20rain%20that%20falls%20on%20Maharashtra%20is%20drained%20away%20because%20of%20the%20type%20of%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Karlekar.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20have%20dug%20pits%20and%20contours%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20all%20the%20water%20that%20falls%20on%20the%20soil%20gets%20absorbed%20into%20aquifers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20too%20has%20seen%20a%20journey%3B%20from%20three%20trees%20in%20a%20deserted%20landscape%20to%20now%201%2C300%20trees%20and%202%2C000%20native%20shrubs.%20There%20are%20many%20pride%20points%20at%20Chavni%2C%20but%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20a%20living%20piece%20of%20history%20tops%20them%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBook%20your%20trip%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fchavni.lohagad%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723101245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-1722509927.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359311%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Located%20near%20Lohagad%20and%20Visapur%20forts%2C%20Chavni%20resort%20in%20Pune%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20was%20created%20by%20Snehal%20Karlekar%2C%20Tushar%20Shetye%2C%20Uday%20Jagtap%2C%20and%20Ajit%20Ingawle.%20It%20celebrates%20Maharashtra's%20cultural%20legacy%20with%20Maratha-style%20accommodations%20and%20eco-conscious%20practices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359311%2Fchavni-maratha-camp-lohagad-visapur-fort-pune-maharashtra-heritage-stay-hotel-sustainable-tents%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UPSC%20CSE%20for%20Hindi-Medium%20Aspirants%3A%20IFS%20Officer%20Shares%20Prep%20Strategy%2C%20Study%20Material%20%26amp%3B%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%2012%20June%202023%2C%20the%20results%20of%20the%20preliminary%20stage%20of%20the%20UPSC-CSE%20were%20scheduled%20to%20be%20announced.%20Unlike%20lakhs%20of%20aspirants%20awaiting%20the%20results%2C%20Vikas%20Kumar%20Meena%20had%20already%20believed%20that%20he%20would%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20list.%20He%20was%20so%20hopeless%20that%20he%20purchased%20the%20course%20for%20another%20competitive%20examination%2C%20minutes%20before%20the%20results%20were%20to%20be%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20confidence%20that%20I%20would%20clear%20the%20prelims.%20I%20was%20so%20unmotivated%20that%20I%20tried%20shifting%20my%20focus%20to%20the%20SSC-CGL%20exam.%20I%20was%20busy%20solving%20the%20previous%20year%20questions%20for%20it%20when%20my%20friend%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20had%20checked%20the%20results.%20I%20was%20so%20scared%20that%20I%20wondered%20how%20I%20would%20face%20my%20family%20and%20relatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20few%20more%20minutes%2C%20I%20somehow%20gathered%20courage%20and%20found%20my%20name%20on%20the%20list.%20I%20checked%20my%20roll%20number%20at%20least%2020%20times.%20The%20happiness%20of%20clearing%20the%20UPSC%20prelims%20gives%20a%20different%20level%20of%20satisfaction%20altogether%20than%20clearing%20all%20subsequent%20stages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20his%20worry%2C%20Vikas%20says%2C%20was%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F235855%2Fupsc-topper-how-tips-method-irs-officer-failed-40-exams-inspiri