ed%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20examination.%20In%202019%2C%20he%20came%20to%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20for%20a%20demo%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20hundreds%20of%20aspirants%20coming%20out%20of%20classes.%20I%20became%20hopeless%20seeing%20this%20crowd%20and%20wondered%20how%20I%20was%20going%20to%20survive%20here.%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20small%20insect%20and%20feared%20losing%20my%20identity%20if%20I%20walked%20into%20that%20crowd%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20graduation%20in%202021%2C%20he%20started%20preparing%20for%20the%20examination.%20He%20clears%20a%20few%20misconceptions%20and%20shares%20helpful%20tips%20for%20aspirants%20based%20on%20his%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Psychological%20barriers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20says%20that%20firstly%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20are%20told%20to%20join%20coaching%20institutes%20because%20without%20it%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20succeed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20psychological%20aspects%20which%20get%20affected%20due%20to%20senior%20culture%20in%20the%20lanes%20of%20Mukherjee%20Nagar.%20New%20candidates%20are%20expected%20to%20seek%20guidance%20from%20those%20who%20have%20already%20given%20multiple%20attempts.%20So%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20%3Cem%3Ebhaiyaji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Esirji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eculture.%20They%20put%20blind%20faith%20in%20them%20and%20consider%20those%20who%20cleared%20the%20exam%20as%20god%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecondly%2C%20most%20of%20these%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20come%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F238088%2Fips-hero-upsc-cse-examination-tips-strategy-free-online-webinar-suraj-singh-parihar-police-instagram-facebook-twitter-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20income%20backgrounds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20T