beyond%20to%20help%20others%2C%20with%20people%20calling%20him%20Batman%20and%20thanking%20him%20for%20everything%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitesh%2C%20a%20student%2C%20took%20Dushyant%E2%80%99s%20help%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20for%20a%20pervert%20who%20was%20flashing%20women%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20He%20was%20able%20to%20register%20a%20complaint%20and%20the%20case%20is%20in%20court%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBroseph%20helped%20us%20with%20all%20the%20details%20about%20filing%20a%20complaint%20and%20what%20evidence%20is%20needed.%20He%20was%20instrumental%20in%20these%20women%20seeking%20justice.%20His%20team%20followed%20up%20with%20us%20and%20helped%20us%20in%20every%20step.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20Batman%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hitesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20would%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20in%20it%20for%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20the%20right%20to%20work%20but%20never%20to%20its%20fruits.%20Let%20not%20the%20fruits%20of%20action%20be%20your%20motive%2C%20nor%20let%20your%20attachment%20be%20to%20inaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20his%20mantra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20candidly%20accepts%20that%20while%20saying%20it%20is%20easy%2C%20there%20are%20difficult%20days.%20But%20knowing%20that%20this%20is%20the%20right%20path%20helps%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSocial%20workers%20should%20forgo%20the%20thought%20of%20any%20personal%20gain%20from%20their%20work.%20This%20work%20is%20strictly%20for%20society%2C%20and%20any%20kind%20of%20expectations%20will%20only%20serve%20to%20bring%20it%20down.%20The%20moment%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20expect%20anything%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20free%20yourself%20up%20to%20truly%20do%20everything.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20I%20go%20by%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20devastation%20at%20Abraham%E2%80%99s%20death%20made%20it%20very%20important%20for%20him%20to%20help%20anyone%20he%20could.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20doing.%20While%20Bengaluru%20is%20swarming%20with%20tech%20bros%2C%20we%20need%20more%20Brosephs%20across%20the%20country.%20Perhaps%20we%20should%20consider%20emulating%20his%20selfless%20actions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20help%20him%2C%20you%20could%20donate%20to%20broseph%40upi.%20You%20can%20also%20join%20his%20army%20by%20visiting%20the%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flinktr.ee%2FSt_Broseph%5C%22%3Ebroseph.in.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%3A%20Dushyant%20Dubey%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723021013000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360074%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20social%20worker%20and%20a%20legend%20on%20Reddit%2C%20Dushyant%20Dubey%20aka%20St%20Broseph%20helps%20people%20solve%20the%20most%20complex%20problems%2C%20ranging%20from%20cyber%20crime%2C%20stalking%2C%20civic%20issues%20to%20domestic%20violence%20and%20more.%20He%20runs%20the%20St%20Broseph%20Foundation%20with%20thousands%20of%20volunteers%20who%20help%20people%20get%20justice%20across%20Bengaluru%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Chennai%20and%20Pune.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Champion%2C%20Always%3A%20Wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%E2%80%99s%20Incredible%20Journey%20to%20Olympics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20is%20disqualified%20from%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Wrestling%2050%20kg%20Class%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Olympics.%20Phogat%20failed%20to%20meet%20the%20weight%20requirements%2C%20being%20100%20grams%20over%20the%20allowable%20weight%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20it%E2%80%99s%20disheartening%20for%20Indians%20and%20f