.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffood-2-1722422772-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359204%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20chicken%20feast%20(L)%20and%20tiger%20prawns%20make%20for%20a%20great%20Sunday%20lunch%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Farida%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20notes%20that%20even%20though%20the%20kitchen%20was%20filled%20with%20a%20large%20number%20of%20women%20cooking%20their%20specialities%2C%20there%20was%20no%20hint%20of%20competition.%20It%20is%20these%20memories%20that%20have%20remained%20in%20the%20folds%20of%20Farida%E2%80%99s%20recipe%20books.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20whatever%20we%20have%20achieved%20at%20Karrylicious%20Kitchen%20is%20because%20of%20our%20roots%20and%20authenticity%20without%20which%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20possible.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParsi%20food%20has%20enjoyed%20an%20itinerant%20history.%20Farida%20underlines%20how%20every%20Parsi%20home%20has%20its%20own%20repository%20of%20culinary%20secrets.%20She%20gestures%20towards%20%3Cem%3Edhansak.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20and%20every%20home%20has%20its%20own%20recipe%20for%20this%20dish.%20And%20the%20taste%20also%20differs%20across%20households%2C%20but%20the%20taste%20quotient%20will%20be%20amazing%20irrespective%20of%20which%20home%20you%20eat%20it%20in.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20taste%20profiles%20also%20change%20across%20generations.%20Farida%20agrees.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20cooking%20I%20used%20to%20stay%20exactly%20true%20to%20my%20great-grandmother%E2%80%99s%20and%20mother%E2%80%99s%20recipes.%20But%20now%20I%20allow%20myself%20a%20little%20variation%2C%20a%20little%20additions%20here%20and%20there%20and%20a%20change%20in%20technique.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20the%20strawberry%20jam%20and%20custard%20cake%20in%